title: [Boreas Ridge, Zephyr Lane]
description: The path begins to ascend the ridge steeply here, layered grooves in the shale bricks providing traction in inclement weather.  Bushes and shrubs hide small gates of iron, steel, and wood that lead to the manors beyond.
